msgstr "Slider image"

msgid "plugins.generic.sliderHome.sliderImageLink"
msgstr "If you want to put a link on the slider image you can provide an URL here."

msgid "plugins.generic.sliderHome.content"
msgstr "Note: The HTML provided here will be wrapped in a &lt;div id=\"slider-overlay\" class=\"slider-text\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; providing a transparent background. You can modify the style from your journal stylesheet. You should not include images here."

