msgid "plugins.generic.sliderHome.contentForm.label"
msgstr "Information for styling slides using CSS"

msgid "plugins.generic.sliderHome.contentForm.description"
msgstr "The appearance of the slider images and HTML overlay can be modified via the journal's CSS stylesheet.<br>The slider images are embedded in an HTML &ltfigure&gt element, which can be selected via the CSS selector figure.slider-figure.<br>Overlay content can be selected via #slider-overlay.slider-text.<br>If no image is uploaded, the overlay content is displayed centered without background. In this case, the HTML element can be selected via #slide-no-image-container or .slide-no-image-container."

